Layer inversion

Capital contamination

C. HIRES (H1‚ÄìH5)
Vesting: 3 years

No equity without role fidelity

Severance: Guaranteed on role mismatch (no-fault)

Forfeiture: Only on documented authority breach

D. BOARD (B1‚ÄìB5)
Minimal equity or stipend

No performance-based upside

Automatic removal if operational involvement occurs

Cooling-off period before any other role

E. COUNCIL (C1‚ÄìC5)
No equity

Fixed-term honoraria

Exit anytime without penalty

Protection from retaliation codified

F. EXIT CLAUSE (SYSTEM-WIDE)
Any member may exit if:

system violates its own constitution

refusal rights are overridden

capital logic dominates upstream layers

Exit includes:

reputational neutrality

retained vested rights

public silence optional, never compelled

