Salary + profit share
Restrictions:

No veto or domain authority beyond role

Class C ‚Äî Domain Stewards / Partners
Ownership:

Steward equity (non-voting or oversight)

No venture equity unless also a worker
Compensation:

Stipends/honoraria for service
Restrictions:

Cannot accumulate governance equity beyond stewardship

Class D ‚Äî Board / Fiduciary Members
Ownership:

None financially
Compensation:

Stipend/honorarium
Restrictions:

No equity, no profit share

Class E ‚Äî Council / Community
Ownership:

None financially
Compensation:

Honoraria for participation
Restrictions:

No equity, no vote

Class F ‚Äî Capital Participants (OVCS LPs, external)
Ownership:

Non-voting capped financial units
Compensation:

Returns up to cap

No governance beyond rights agreements

