II. MEMBER EQUITY AGREEMENT (DRAFT ‚Äî CORE TERMS)
Agreement Name: Cooperative Membership & Equity Participation Agreement

1. Membership Grant
Member is admitted as Class [A/B/C/D/E] with rights strictly limited to that class.

2. Equity Type
Membership Units (non-transferable)

Redeemable at formula value

No speculative appreciation promise

3. Vesting
Time-based only

Pauses upon boundary breach

No acceleration for control or exits

4. Compensation
Wages/salary (if applicable)

Patronage dividends proportional to labor or contribution

No guaranteed distributions

5. Governance Limits
Member acknowledges:

No cross-domain authority

No implied management rights

No narrative or representational authority

6. Exit
Voluntary exit permitted anytime

Vested units redeemed per formula

No non-compete

Confidentiality limited to trade secrets (no gag on critique)

7. Dissolution
Member has no claim on Commons Capital

Residual assets flow per bylaws

(This agreement is standard coop law with added boundary clauses; nothing exotic.)

