Internal capital accounts

Redeemable, capped returns

Best for: Scaling labor-intensive ops

3. Program-Related Investments (PRI)
From foundations

Low interest, long-term

Best for: Platforms, Umoya-adjacent work

4. Commons Bonds
Fixed return

Paid from surplus only

No control rights

Best for: Infrastructure, land, factories

5. Strategic Customers (Prepay / Offtake)
Advance purchase agreements

No financial control

Best for: Food, manufacturing, logistics

