Accrued wages	400,000
Deferred revenue	600,000
Reserves	2,000,000
Member equity	3,200,000
Total Liabilities & Equity	7,000,000
Runway

Operating cushion = Reserves / Monthly burn

Monthly burn ~ 1.2M

Runway = ~1.7 months without revenue

But evolving surplus makes runway positive long-term.

