Recommended language (pick one, depending on appetite):

Option A ‚Äî Public Domain‚ÄìEquivalent (Strongest)

‚ÄúThese materials are dedicated to the public domain to the fullest extent permitted by law. No rights are reserved.‚Äù

Option B ‚Äî CC0 1.0 Universal (Practical)

‚ÄúThis work is released under CC0 1.0 Universal.‚Äù

