It‚Äôs more dangerous than explicit governance.

IMPLICATION 4 ‚Äî FAILURE CASCADES BECOME POSSIBLE
Right now, your architecture is anti-cascade.

Kernel firms reintroduce cascade risk.

If DESEF:

becomes captured

becomes politicized

becomes legally constrained

becomes financially dependent

becomes symbolically authoritative

Then:

downstream ventures hesitate

pilots self-censor

forks weaken

